<co-content>
 <p variant="body1">
  Hey Learner!
 </p>
 <p variant="body1">
  Excited about this course? Join the DeepLearning.AI  Forum to:
 </p>
 <ul bullettype="bullets">
  <li>
   <p variant="body1">
    <strong>
     Report
    </strong>
    any trouble with assignments
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p variant="body1">
    <strong>
     Get support
    </strong>
    for any technical issues you might have with the course/platform
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p variant="body1">
    <strong>
     Look for guidance
    </strong>
    on any questions you might have about the course
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p variant="body1">
    <strong>
     Chat with others:
    </strong>
    Share ideas, ask questions, and discuss AI.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p variant="body1">
    <strong>
     Work together:
    </strong>
    Collaborate on AI projects and build something awesome.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p variant="body1">
    <strong>
     Stay in the loop:
    </strong>
    Get updates on courses, events, and AI news.
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p variant="body1">
  Click on
  <a href="https://bit.ly/44cz8nG" title="">
   <strong>
    this link
   </strong>
  </a>
  to create your free account and connect with the global AI community!
 </p>
 <p variant="body1">
  - The DeepLearning.AI team
 </p>
 <p>
 </p>
</co-content>
